      "kurukh_word": "Minkhnā",
      "kurukh_word_ascii": "Minkhna",
      "english_definition": "kan, yan, to close the eyes. Khan minkhnā, to shut the eyes; said also of the closing of flowers, pūmp minkhyā, the flower closed itself.",
